column1: #Text=Chicago Tribune - Trump supremacy emboldens Swedish populists.
#Text=Ingen internationell tidning har skrivit om Svetsaren...just saying.

#Text="The leftist and liberal establishment, with open borders, free immigration, that nation states should be removed -- all of that -- there's never been any popular support for that but they've managed to dominate the western world for decades," he said.
#Text=While sharing Trump's views on immigration, Akesson doesn't agree on trade.
#Text="If capital has an interest in open borders, I don't have a problem with that," he said.
#Text="I believe in free trade -- I think that's great.

#Text=Carl Bildt, a former prime minister who served as foreign minister in the government ousted two years ago, wrote in the Washington Post last month that Trump's victory could mark the end of the west as we know it.".

column1: #Text="It's the end of Carl Bildt's world," he said.
#Text="He's one of Sweden's foremost globalists and biggest deniers of the nation state and national identity.
